{"tid":346901,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇鬥慘呢個行為？","createTime":"2017-08-04T10:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T14:35:55.000Z","uid":9191,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8146971a1cdffb597242cd2017138f0bbafa44ff","tid":346901,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:41:40.000Z","msg":"「你已經好好架啦，我呢&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n「我都係啊，我&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n唔同嘅人有唔同嘅問題，其實好多時簡單地幾句安慰下就夠，或者停止放負轉下話題都得，可以嘅話真係設身處地諗下佢地嘅真實情況，但往往最撚worse嘅係無端鬥慘，完全忽視唒人地嘅情況。<br />\n<br />\n各位點睇呢個行為？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e45daaa1816b42f8752edcd011edc7f28e9824","tid":346901,"uid":9191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:44:56.000Z","msg":"舉個而家社會俾人舉得幾多下嘅例子，就係而家啲後生抗疫力低，話乜野其實比起以前已經好好多。<br />\n但實際上，而家後生要面對嘅情況已經係更加高層次，講求嘅係唔同能力上嘅考驗，加上唔同社會嘅問題壓迫，而引致嘅心理壓力已經係比起以前嘅複雜程度高好多。<br />\n用返某一代嘅思維去套入呢一代，係完全不負責任/唔經大腦嘅表現。"},{"pid":"5c99a6baf73486ee9485f00654f67b071547b09a","tid":346901,"uid":37153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:45:22.000Z","msg":"奉旨要安慰你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己呻得人地就唔講得"},{"pid":"1302f82d7018d36f1501256c7039b65dcc34ea78","tid":346901,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:46:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>奉旨要安慰你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己呻得人地就唔講得</blockquote><br />\n好多時唔等於一定要 我個睇法純粹拋下磚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"059d2a1406701bbac060a4cc9214947ee4858f6d","tid":346901,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:49:05.000Z","msg":"我覺得有啲幼稚，通常都係啲自我嘅人先會咁做。不過唔排除有啲人咁做係想令到對方覺得佢渡過緊嘅唔係剩係得佢一個人，有人陪住佢。不過如果純粹想鬥慘而鬥慘，真係好唔成熟好自我。覺得依個世界除左佢都唔會有人傷心<br />\n<br />\n利申，好鍾意同人鬥慘"},{"pid":"0a0178ddad50dd1e0c1af20af7f69e93430462e3","tid":346901,"uid":11698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:49:39.000Z","msg":"講自己情況慘啲<br />\n<br />\n想佢覺得低處未算低啫"},{"pid":"e38f9bbb54d253a713e2332cde6d0917efa18d4c","tid":346901,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:50:21.000Z","msg":"或者咁講 點回應第一個人呻係個人意願 純粹想針對以鬥慘作為回應嘅討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"971466db99422e69554d1ddb7d61ab22cfe092c7","tid":346901,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:54:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得有啲幼稚，通常都係啲自我嘅人先會咁做。不過唔排除有啲人咁做係想令到對方覺得佢渡過緊嘅唔係剩係得佢一個人，有人陪住佢。不過如果純粹想鬥慘而鬥慘，真係好唔成熟好自我。覺得依個世界除左佢都唔會有人傷心<br />\n<br />\n利申，好鍾意同人鬥慘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>講自己情況慘啲<br />\n<br />\n想佢覺得低處未算低啫</blockquote><br />\n即係I feel the same嗰類 I see <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f450cb83866704b630074be47aaa435ccfce92eb","tid":346901,"uid":45966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T11:03:12.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"42241253757c69b2ea683379925d18a66bbb1f0f","tid":346901,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T18:52:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9241ef2c0d5333ee516cec3e163ab9f8e76a881f","tid":346901,"uid":75707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T18:55:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講自己情況慘啲<br />\n<br />\n想佢覺得低處未算低啫</blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0841e56ed89f0a567273be62fdb66065f4c124a","tid":346901,"uid":75707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T18:55:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講自己情況慘啲<br />\n<br />\n想佢覺得低處未算低啫</blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但原來你地覺得咁樣係鬥慘 安慰人真係好難啊屌你老母"},{"pid":"e3f31876d5cd7f4ac1ec8a9bd5437fcef1b030a3","tid":346901,"uid":72638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T18:56:26.000Z","msg":"可能都係想呻下姐<br />\n講左出黎會舒服啲"},{"pid":"58b59bf8cddf150024096c5a3ef73d64ef66878e","tid":346901,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T19:05:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能都係想呻下姐<br />\n講左出黎會舒服啲</blockquote><br />\n但如果以真係「鬥」個心態去出發又點睇？<br />\n即係唔同純粹分享下 而係感覺到對方有意圖地「鬥」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e81d877191c445a63b60987d60c6e8258b87920","tid":346901,"uid":72638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T19:11:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可能都係想呻下姐<br />\n講左出黎會舒服啲</blockquote><br />\n但如果以真係「鬥」個心態去出發又點睇？<br />\n即係唔同純粹分享下 而係感覺到對方有意圖地「鬥」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同佢講 你最慘<br />\nok you win <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e597190a8935581dc4b3ddff47e4f999c9870c2","tid":346901,"uid":113429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T19:16:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6840df25404c61670b658aedb251b1ca5ce781c5","tid":346901,"uid":113429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T19:18:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55619ba3d85efc582df297e417e91ab708d6f66b","tid":346901,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T19:19:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可能都係想呻下姐<br />\n講左出黎會舒服啲</blockquote><br />\n但如果以真係「鬥」個心態去出發又點睇？<br />\n即係唔同純粹分享下 而係感覺到對方有意圖地「鬥」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同佢講 你最慘<br />\nok you win <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nI see<br />\n好多時呢啲情況第一個真係有情感需要呻嗰位 就係因為呢啲鬥嘅行為最後不了了之 成為咗諗唔開嘅導火線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85623348bff2cfb15dbde109a2726f6961cc653","tid":346901,"uid":126766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T19:21:10.000Z","msg":"有d人透過鬥慘<br />\n去特顯自己比你吃得苦<br />\n繼而心入面果句就係：你呻乜撚姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好鄙視呢個行為..."},{"pid":"94213e6afa5c32c0b6f5b920446dba4b3faef6b1","tid":346901,"uid":113429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T19:21:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa1df1303076c6d0a84c7abfa102d5d1ddb62463","tid":346901,"uid":126766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T19:23:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有d人透過鬥慘<br />\n去特顯自己比你吃得苦<br />\n繼而心入面果句就係：你呻乜撚姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好鄙視呢個行為...</blockquote><br />\n好似你俾人打十巴好撚痛，我俾人打一巴就會唔痛咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我ex就係咁<br />\n成日同佢呻之後就會鬥慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我就廢撚事同佢傾"},{"pid":"a24f06e4d836d3e07b1418c1741cab31d808e6fd","tid":346901,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T19:24:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無意義，唔同背景性格嘅人面對唔同嘅事感覺都唔同，好多野都冇辦法純粹地去比較</blockquote><br />\n不過如果唔係鬥嘅方式，係幾好嘅安慰方式，見到人地慘過自己就會即刻冇咁sad心理平衡好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n往往好多時後者嘅情況會比較少或者唔係少 係因為好難搵個平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身嗰個人要有一定嘅技巧先會平衡到 令到當事人唔會覺得係鬥慘之餘 仲有安慰嘅成分<br />\n同埋當事人本身個心理可能都會有誤解個原意 <br />\n兩個情況令到提出自己更差/類似嘅情況嘅時候 真係有安慰作用係比較少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb9834ad29983992d5363a28abbcb07bc093264","tid":346901,"uid":105688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T19:26:20.000Z","msg":"其他人既問題唔係問題，我既問題先係問題，而且要趁住呢個機會比所有人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n或者咁講：sympathy whore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4bdb568af8f5516e27d1fdecc243bd9526cdae","tid":346901,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T19:26:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有d人透過鬥慘<br />\n去特顯自己比你吃得苦<br />\n繼而心入面果句就係：你呻乜撚姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好鄙視呢個行為...</blockquote><br />\n好似你俾人打十巴好撚痛，我俾人打一巴就會唔痛咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢種就係我想講嗰個原意<br />\n每一個人都有唔同嘅情況 唔可以以自己個價值觀去衡量黎證明邊個慘啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb3b1ed0965b0d170b17c35817b1377592dc0ee","tid":346901,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T04:54:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}